title: I Choose Victorinox - Kari Underly
transcripts:
[MUSIC PLAYING] 

I'm a third generation master butcher on both sides of my family and oddly enough both of my grandmothers were in the trade of butchery so it's just something that's in my blood. Victorinox has been in my family for years. It's the tools that we've always used and I just can't see using any other knife. I need a tool that's hardworking, honest, and a lot of integrity because if I don't trust that knife, me cutting is a dangerous job. I like a knife that just really kinda melts in your hand that's just an extension of you. That's just always been what I used and again I can't use anything else. I'm Kari Underly, author, master butcher, and the principle of range ing  and I choose Victorinox.
